{"tid":336589,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"chenglap：沒人要打掉那「釋法權」的話, 基本法違反不違反的, 真的重要嗎?","createTime":"2017-07-26T14:20:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-27T05:46:45.000Z","uid":47714,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"47537cd238b7e91bbd4c68274ff8b564ff9d0f04","tid":336589,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T14:20:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/cheng.lap.9/posts/10155457382627357\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcheng.lap.9%2Fposts%2F10155457382627357&d=1K44EpHTQQrBuQJGfAxDoe9M5Ue6CDmcYDZznX2R1Ws%3D&h=aa91f770\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.facebook.com/cheng.lap.9/posts/10155457382627357</a><br />\n<br />\n作者：chenglap<br />\n<br />\n其實當別人說這怎樣違反基本法時, 我在想, 如果沒有人提出要打掉那個「釋法權」的話, 甚麼違反不違反的, 真的重要嗎?"},{"pid":"d0cd5927df0956c1f04a827838506bf44dc6c545","tid":336589,"uid":47714,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T14:29:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/cheng.lap.9/posts/10155457390702357\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcheng.lap.9%2Fposts%2F10155457390702357&d=1K44EpHTQQrBuQJGfAxDoe9M5Ue6CDmcYDZznX2R1Ws%3D&h=1a9941cb\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.facebook.com/cheng.lap.9/posts/10155457390702357</a><br />\n<br />\n作者：chenglap<br />\n<br />\n基本法的「釋法權」就像叮噹大富翁裡的「處境掉換槍」一樣, 他就是有一個規則足以架空所有其他規則.<br />\n<br />\n這就好像說, 用當歸, 蓮子, 海馬, 天山雪蓮和人參, 五碗水煮成一碗水, 慢火煎三小時, 然後不要喝倒了它.<br />\n<br />\n又或者基本法就是一鍋粥裡有乾貝, 瘦肉, 咸蛋, 花生, 鮑魚等名貴材料, 再加一篤屎. 那篤屎存在之後, 你討論裡面的鮑魚有幾多個頭是否有意義?"},{"pid":"8748e8a06ba9b4ee169756a9232f117206cb9598","tid":336589,"uid":61517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T21:38:25.000Z","msg":"正解"},{"pid":"0e76a6e5af7e0c816cd5a35c4d4017491651e61c","tid":336589,"uid":35790,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T22:05:15.000Z","msg":"釋法權及單程證係中國治港兩大神棍"},{"pid":"48e8c13200b9110dae4f98dd587a19cf5d775076","tid":336589,"uid":130105,"